<<.from-version "5.5.0">> Colour operators are [[filter operators|Filter Operators]] that manipulate CSS colour values. They are backed by the [[color.js|https://colorjs.io/]] library, and support wide gamut colours such as Display P3. See ColourPalettes for background.

